African Rainbow Says Full-Year Earnings Ex-Items Rose 94% to $470 Million

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-08-31T05:09:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-31/african-rainbow-says-full-year-earnings-ex-items-rose-94-to-470-million.html
African Rainbow Minerals Ltd. (ARI)  said
earnings excluding one-time items surged 94 percent to 3.32
billion rand in the year through June.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
